trans-unit.source: Describes how to use the extension to import salary and wage transactions from the Quickbooks Payroll service.

trans-unit.source: The Quickbooks Payroll File Import Extension to Business Central

seg-source.mrk: The Quickbooks Payroll File Import Extension to Business Central

target.mrk: Rozšíření Quickbooks Payroll File Import do Business Central

trans-unit.source: To account for salary payments and related transactions, you must import and post financial transactions made by your payroll provider to the general ledger.

seg-source.mrk: To account for salary payments and related transactions, you must import and post financial transactions made by your payroll provider to the general ledger.

target.mrk: Chcete-li účtovat platby mezd a související transakce, musíte importovat a zaúčtovat finanční transakce provedené poskytovatelem mezd do hlavní knihy.

trans-unit.source: To do this, you first import a file that you receive from the payroll provider into the **General Journal** window.

seg-source.mrk: To do this, you first import a file that you receive from the payroll provider into the **General Journal** window.

target.mrk: Pro provedení, nejprve importujte soubor, který obdržíte od poskytovatele mezd do okna **Hlavní deník**.

trans-unit.source: Then you map the external accounts in the payroll file to the relevant G/L accounts.

seg-source.mrk: Then you map the external accounts in the payroll file to the relevant G/L accounts.

target.mrk: Poté namapujete externí účty v souboru mezd na příslušné finanční účty.

trans-unit.source: Lastly, you post the payroll transactions according to the account mapping.

seg-source.mrk: Lastly, you post the payroll transactions according to the account mapping.

target.mrk: Nakonec zaúčtujete mzdové transakce podle mapování účtu.

trans-unit.source: The Quickbooks Payroll File Import extension allows you to import payroll transaction from the Quickbooks Payroll service.

seg-source.mrk: The Quickbooks Payroll File Import extension allows you to import payroll transaction from the Quickbooks Payroll service.

target.mrk: Rozšíření Quickbooks Payroll File Import vám umožňuje importovat transakce mezd ze služby Quickbooks Payroll service.
